        template: "function `{name}` references atlas L node `{node_id}` in its body but has no @implements citation",
        explain: "A function body cites one or more L nodes (via L[id] expressions) but the function declares no `@implements` annotation. Adding `@implements(L[id])` records the law-of-record so downstream verification (S6/S7 prover) can attach proofs to the right node.",
        fix_it_kind: FixItKind::Insert
